parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp^.Finally a chance to put that jerk in his place…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp^.Plus, it’ll be an easy win in front of Melissa.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe^.When she sees how I kick his ass, maybe she’ll think twice about the value I bring to this place.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe^.What the hell caused those two to meet up?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.I bet they are talking about me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.I’m being paranoid. Andrea is Melissa’s boss…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe^.The only thing I know for sure, it’s going to piss Melissa off that I’m butting into their workout meeting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.If I had landed a punch, he’d be out cold!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp^.Why did I try so hard to impress Melissa?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.I should have just waited for him to make the first move.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp^.I guess I should take a shower.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Damn. These walls are thin. I can hear Melissa on the other side.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShClNo1#>.Is this a peephole into the women’s shower?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOp#>.I can see right through into the other shower!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.I should have known a cop would do something like this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMaOp.I bet Bobby did this himself. That creep!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.David said you’ve been in here a long time. Is everything okay?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaOp.I was just spending some time alone. Not many people come in here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Do you feel safe? Do you need any help?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoOp.I… I want to see you again. But I need more time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.Don’t leave me alone here… At least not into the night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I won’t be that long… I’ll come back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.In the meantime, do you want to leave the women’s locker room?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoEx.You better get out of here before someone sees you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.And you don’t worry enough… David suspects something.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I’m not surprised. He did see you naked at the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Even more of a reason to keep our distance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoEx.Don’t let his demeanor fool you. He’s a clever man…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoCl.He notices us both away at the same time, he’ll start snooping around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Get dressed and get out of here… You still have to clean my condo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlEx.You got your sex, now you owe me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Did you make a peephole into the other shower room, Bobby?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlEx.Does it matter who did it? You enjoyed the show, didn’t you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.You continue to confirm my opinion about you and your squad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlEx.I worry about you, 1Hero. No fighting skills, and no libido…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlDe.Maybe you should look into testosterone therapy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.There’s a super strong stream of water coming out of the plumbing!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I wonder if there is a way to shut it off.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.What the hell was that all about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.Something wrong with the men’s shower room, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrCl.Oh, uh… I was just having a brief chat with Melissa before hitting the shower.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl^.Shit. I better be careful not to piss off Andrea…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp^.As fun as it is to tease Melissa.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp^.Holy shit! Andrea must really trust me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp^.I better stay focused and trust my instincts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp^.If I can solve this case, it’s sure to impress her…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp^.I better get to the church and keep an eye on Brian and Judy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaDe^.Judy’s got a lot of work on her hands to clean up that room of hers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I shouldn’t be trying to spy on Andrea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.This electrical box controls the power to the gym.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.This electrical box controls the power to the gym.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.If I install the dimmer in this electrical box, I can lower the voltage to the gym… I wonder what that would do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Did I do that? How do I put out the fire?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Come back soon… But leave me for now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.No, 1Hero. A weight has been lifted… I do not fear what we’ve become.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I like you too, Judy. But what about the church? What about your faith in God?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoOp.Why is it you do not have faith in God?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I mean… Maybe I do… I’ve seen some shit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrAg.Maybe the world could be better. A world where we could be together, without worry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Imagine a world where we could love each other freely… all of us, together.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaAg.Nothing but pleasure for the rest of our days!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe.Judy, you’re scaring me. This isn’t you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I’m sorry if I’ve caused you to have a crisis of faith…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.But Lilith is not the answer to our problems.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Fortunately, someone’s here to help me convince you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx>.It’s been fun. But we’ve gotten what we need.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.It’s okay, 1Hero. Everything will be fine in the end.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnCl.Very funny. Come back and unlock these cuffs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShCl.Judy! Kimberly! You’re just going to leave me here like this?!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMaCl.How the hell am I going to get out of this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaOp.Whoo, I’m looking forward to changing out of uniform and getting some good exercise.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnCl.Smooth moves, pervert! You gave away your secret!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlOp.What are you doing cuffed in the women’s changing room?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnCl.Maybe you could try unlocking these cuffs?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.With an attitude like that? Why should I?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlDe.I’m thinking a better idea is to bring everyone by to see the show.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMaClNo1.And I’ll tell the whole world you watched it through the peephole.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.Listen here, Canmore. You’ve got a lot of nerve.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoMaDeNo1.No, Canmore! It’s your turn to listen! It’s time someone put you in your place, and I’ve been waiting a long time for this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnOp.From the day you got here, you made it clear you think you’re better than everyone else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnOp.Ignoring what you’re told, going off to do your own thing…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.People talk. We all know the score with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnOp.Despite your constant insubordination, Kimura gave you a chance and you blew it because you can’t stop fucking around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.And usually, officers have to go through a lot of training before they’re allowed to go out armed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.Not just a little target practice. Tests, learning rules, and let’s not forget the most important part: safety lessons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.You could kill someone with that thing, you know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.With all the free passes you get, did you learn some humility and gratitude?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.Nope, not Detective Canmore. He just takes it in stride that he deserves it all.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnOp.Hold on, I think something’s wrong with my ears. Let me clear them out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaCl.I’ve been ungrateful and arrogant. I keep making a lot of mistakes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaCl.I’m sorry I’ve been such a jerk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaDe.Come clean with me, Canmore… What the hell is going on with you and Kimura?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Something big is happening, Bobby… Kimura won’t be here much longer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.The Guild case isn’t over… In fact, it’s far more complex than you probably realize.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.You think I don’t know that? You think my men get called away from the mansion without explanation and I don’t get suspicious?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I might need help from you and your men.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I need to go… Guild goons are going to try and take over the Channel 4 building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.But… They are not normal henchmen… They will be very hard to take down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Listen, Bobby. Kimura doesn’t know about any of this. She’s leaving the country.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Pull together some men and meet at the Channel 4 building. And be quiet about it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.And besides, if you don’t help me, I’ll tell the whole office about the peephole.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Well… This will probably backfire… But what choice do we have?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoClNo1^.What the hell!? Where did my amulet go?...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.Shit… That means Lillian will have all three…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlOp.This is the ladies room, 1Hero… Did you make a wrong turn?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I won and now we’re going to fuck.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.We most certainly are not! Are you crazy?");
